MARVEL's superheroes from India or Indian descent;
Spider-Man (Pavitr Prabhakar), Omega Sentinel (Karima Shapandar), Giant-Man (Raz Malhotra), Cerebra (Shakti Haddad), Indra (Paras Gavaskar), Thunderbird (Neal Shaara),Timeslip (Rina Patel), Trinary (Shilpa Khatri), Vesper (Raani Jatwinder) & Sapna (name unknown).  The *Daevas* (Hindu Gods) are represented in MARVEL.

